1. *Brodovi* su pristajali u luci cijele noći. (Ships were docking in the port all night.)
2. Kao dijete, imao sam čitavu kolekciju *brodova* od lego kockica. (As a child, I had a whole collection of Lego *ships*.)
3. U gradu se održava velika izložba *brodova* iz različitih perioda. (A large exhibition of *ships* from different periods is taking place in the city.)
4. Kapetan je bio ponosan na svoju posadu i njihovu sposobnost da upravljaju velikim *brodovima*. (The captain was proud of his crew and their ability to handle large *ships*.)
5. Vozili smo se uz obalu i gledali *brodove* koji su plovili rijekom. (We drove along the coast and watched the *ships* sailing down the river.)
6. Nakon popravka, *brod* je krenuo dalje prema svojoj destinaciji. (After repairs, the *ship* continued on its journey.)
7. Kapetan je provjerio svaki detalj prije nego što je dao naredbu za isplovljavanje *broda*. (The captain checked every detail before giving the order to sail the *ship*.)
8. Kraj obale je bila nasukana olupina *broda* koja je ondje stajala godinama. (At the shore was a stranded wreck of a *ship* that had been there for years.)
9. Našao sam se na palubi *broda* koji je plovio dubokim oceanom. (I found myself on the deck of a *ship* sailing the deep ocean.)
10. Radnici su utovarivali teret na *brodove* koji su bili privezani uz dok. (The workers were loading cargo onto the *ships* docked at the pier.)